Returns 400 on failure, 200 on success (returns the order model).

         *  1. If count(erros) == count(order->elements), cancel the whole order, we can't fix it. Say `ACTION_NOT_SUPPORTED`
         *  2. Otherwise, remove the problematic elements from the order.
         *  3. Fix the invoice at the end of it all.
